name: ONIMATA - VOL.04
description:
VOL.04 "MISBELIEF"

This fight is impossible to avoid. Everyone is going all out with their own skill. TEIKO is fighting for their belief of fighting the law, while the gang is fighting to defend themselves. The gang believes this is just a misunderstanding so they tried to stop TEIKO from being so violent with whatever they have. They even let released their own GOFU (the yellow thing with red colored writing attached to them) to reach the full power.

The fight stops because there's a tremendous power coming out from someone. Whose power is it?
